  "text": "In [CITATION_1] , Gan-Gao introduce the idea of a genuine distinguished character χ 0 of Z(T ). We do not recall the full definition, but wish to clarify the case of Sp 2r (F ) as the choice of distinguished character affects the Satake parameter attached to an unramified principal series representation. While there are 4 distinct distinguished characters for Sp 2r (F ), only two of them, χ 0 + and χ 0 − , are unramified. Here, setting y i = 2α ∨ i , these characters are determined by",
